Introduction

Yina, also known as DJ Ina is a South Korean singer and DJ under Gaon Entertainment. She is a former member of the girl groups AiRiSU and Pocket Girls as Yina and TWEETY under the stage name Yuriel. She made her solo debut on November 30, 2018 with her first digital single "Without You". As of July 31st, 2019, she has become a DJ under the name DJ Ina.
